Class ViewDocumentRequestBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hp.autonomy.hod.client.api.analysis.viewdocument.ViewDocumentRequestBuilder

  • public class ViewDocumentRequestBuilder
extends Object
    Helper class for building up optional parameters for the Query Text Index API. The default value for all parameters is null. Null parameters will not be sent to HP Haven OnDemand
